data.event: 1689 The future county is explored by Spaniards, including Alonso De León.

event.title: 1825 Martín De León of Mexico establishes

data.event: 1825 Martín De León of Mexico establishes a ranch near the old La Salle fort.
1831 Linnville becomes the first Anglo settlement, established by Irish-born merchant, statesman, soldier John J. Linn.
